<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<title>Chai Sutta | Fresh Chai & Snacks</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
    scroll-behavior:smooth;
}

body{
    background:#faf6f0;
    color:#333;
}

a{
    text-decoration:none;
}

header{
    position:fixed;
    width:100%;
    top:0;
    left:0;
    background:#4e2f1b;
    color:#fff;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:space-between;
    align-items:center;
    padding:18px 10%;
    z-index:1000;
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#ffce73;
}

nav a{
    color:white;
    margin-left:25px;
    font-weight:500;
    transition:.3s;
}

nav a:hover{
    color:#ffce73;
}

.hero{
    height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,.55),rgba(0,0,0,.55)),
    url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1511920170033-f8396924c348?auto=format&fit=crop&w=1400&q=80') center/cover;
    display:flex;
    align-items:center;
    justify-content:center;
    text-align:center;
    color:white;
    padding:20px;
}

.hero h1{
    font-size:60px;
    margin-bottom:15px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:20px;
    margin-bottom:30px;
}

.btn{
    background:#ffb347;
    color:#333;
    padding:15px 35px;
    border-radius:30px;
    font-weight:600;
    transition:.3s;
}

.btn:hover{
    background:#fff;
}

section{
    padding:90px 10%;
}

.section-title{
    text-align:center;
    font-size:38px;
    color:#4e2f1b;
    margin-bottom:50px;
}

.menu-grid{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(250px,1fr));
    gap:25px;
}

.menu-card{
    background:white;
    border-radius:15px;
    padding:25px;
    box-shadow:0 8px 20px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
    transition:.3s;
}

.menu-card:hover{
    transform:translateY(-8px);
}

.menu-card h3{
    color:#4e2f1b;
    margin-bottom:10px;
}

.price{
    color:#d97706;
    font-size:22px;
    font-weight:bold;
}

.about{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
    gap:40px;
    align-items:center;
}

.about img{
    width:100%;
    border-radius:20px;
}

.about-text p{
    margin-top:15px;
    line-height:1.8;
}

.testimonial{
    background:#4e2f1b;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    border-radius:20px;
    padding:60px 30px;
}

.testimonial p{
    font-size:22px;
    font-style:italic;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

.contact{
    display:grid;
    grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(300px,1fr));
    gap:40px;
}

form{
    display:flex;
    flex-direction:column;
}

input,textarea{
    padding:15px;
    margin-bottom:18px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:#fff;
    box-shadow:0 5px 10px rgba(0,0,0,.08);
}

textarea{
    resize:none;
    height:140px;
}

button{
    border:none;
    padding:15px;
    background:#4e2f1b;
    color:white;
    border-radius:10px;
    font-size:16px;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:.3s;
}

button:hover{
    background:#d97706;
}

footer{
    background:#2b170d;
    color:white;
    text-align:center;
    padding:25px;
}

@media(max-width:768px){

.hero h1{
    font-size:42px;
}

.hero p{
    font-size:18px;
}

nav{
    display:none;
}

}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<header>

<div class="logo">☕ Chai Sutta</div>

<nav>
<a href="#menu">Menu</a>
<a href="#about">About</a>
<a href="#reviews">Reviews</a>
<a href="#contact">Contact</a>
</nav>

</header>

<section class="hero">

<div>

<h1>Every Sip Tells a Story</h1>

<p>Authentic Indian chai, delicious snacks, and warm conversations served fresh every day.</p>

<a href="#menu" class="btn">Explore Menu</a>

</div>

</section>

<section id="menu">

<h2 class="section-title">Our Menu</h2>

<div class="menu-grid">

<div class="menu-card">
<h3>Masala Chai</h3>
<p>Classic spiced tea brewed fresh.</p>
<div class="price">₹40</div>
</div>

<div class="menu-card">
<h3>Elaichi Chai</h3>
<p>Rich cardamom-flavored chai.</p>
<div class="price">₹45</div>
</div>

<div class="menu-card">
<h3>Ginger Chai</h3>
<p>Refreshing chai with fresh ginger.</p>
<div class="price">₹50</div>
</div>

<div class="menu-card">
<h3>Cold Coffee</h3>
<p>Chilled creamy coffee delight.</p>
<div class="price">₹90</div>
</div>

<div class="menu-card">
<h3>Veg Sandwich</h3>
<p>Grilled sandwich with fresh veggies.</p>
<div class="price">₹120</div>
</div>

<div class="menu-card">
<h3>Samosa (2 pcs)</h3>
<p>Crispy golden potato samosas.</p>
<div class="price">₹60</div>
</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="about">

<h2 class="section-title">About Us</h2>

<div class="about">

<img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509042239860-f550ce710b93?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80" alt="Cafe">

<div class="about-text">

<h3>Where Chai Meets Conversations</h3>

<p>
At Chai Sutta, we believe every cup of chai brings people together. Our café serves handcrafted teas, delicious snacks, and a cozy atmosphere perfect for catching up with friends, working remotely, or simply relaxing.
</p>

<p>
From traditional Indian flavors to modern café favorites, every item is prepared with care and served with a smile.
</p>

</div>

</div>

</section>

<section id="reviews">

<h2 class="section-title">Customer Love</h2>

<div class="testimonial">

<p>
"The best chai I've had in town! Cozy ambiance, tasty snacks, and friendly staff. A perfect place to unwind after a busy day."
</p>

<h3>— Priya Sharma</h3>

</div>

</section>

<section id="contact">

<h2 class="section-title">Contact Us</h2>

<div class="contact">

<div>

<h3>Visit Chai Sutta</h3>

<p><strong>📍 Address:</strong> MG Road, Your City</p>

<p><strong>📞 Phone:</strong> +91 98765 43210</p>

<p><strong>📧 Email:</strong> hello@chaisutta.com</p>

<p style="margin-top:20px;">
We'd love to hear from you! Send us your message or visit our café for a warm cup of chai.
</p>

</div>

<form>

<input type="text" placeholder="Your Name" required>

<input type="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>

<textarea placeholder="Your Message"></textarea>

<button type="submit">Send Message</button>

</form>

</div>

</section>

<footer>

<p>© 2026 Chai Sutta. Made with ❤️ & Fresh Chai.</p>

</footer>

</body>
</html>
